Summary: Bright starlike object dissapears from view quickly
divs: sighting detailsafter reporting an earlier sighting of a "moving star," i returned outside and was astonished as before i even got the digital camera open, an object from the sw sky came out of no where and instead of starting as "star-like" it was bright as a headlight and quickly dimmed as it moved directly n. within 30 seconds it was so dim it faded from view. it was lower in altitude then the other object from less than 1\2 an hour ago. i have viewed the video and the object dimmed to quickly to show up on a weak digital camera.
